               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18490409-name-1107" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18490409-name-1107" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18490409-name-1107" type="surname" value="VERNON"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18490409-name-1107" type="given" value="WILLIAM"></interp>WILLIAM VERNON</persName>
                  </hi>. The prisoner was in my service nearly five months, and was going away on 9th April, in consequence of what my wife said to me—I told her to have the boxes searched—I saw this scarf taken from her box in her presence; it is my daughter's, who is ten years old; also a baby's night dress, which is my property—the other things were taken from her box before I got to the room; they are all my property—the prisoner did not say anything.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18490409-name-1108" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18490409-name-1108" type="gender" value="female"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18490409-name-1108" type="surname" value="VERNON"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18490409-name-1108" type="given" value="EMMA"></interp>EMMA VERNON</persName>
                  </hi>. I am the prosecutor's wife—the prisoner sent for me early in the morning to look at her boxes—when she was going away, and the boxes were corded up, I felt one box, and was certain it was heavier than it ought to be—it was opened in her and Rutherford's presence, and this feather bed and all this property (<hi rend="italic">produced</hi>) found in it.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner. Q.</hi> Is the bed your property? <hi rend="italic">A.</hi> Yes; it was what you used to sleep on—she said she was very sorry she had taken it, she had had a little drop to drink.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18490409-name-1109" type="witnessName">
