                        <interp inst="t18490409-name-1109" type="given" value="ANN"></interp>ANN RUTHERFORD</persName>
                  </hi>. I am also in Mr. Vernon's service, and was present when the box was searched—I saw the bed found; it is Mr. Vernon's pro<lb></lb>perty; and the baby's bed-gown too—I know it by having a mark on it.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner's Defence.</hi> The bed is my own—master's bed is there still</p>
